data.description: Outstanding 2015 Double-wide home (32 x 48) With 3 bedroom and 2 baths, on 2 lots! A great starter home or    or get-away home very close to Lake Livingston- 0.5 miles to private boat launch for home owners only. Home comes with ALL appliances including washer/dryer and microwave. Also includes all kitchen utensils.  Recently fenced  (3 sides) and a new front porch. storage shed, gravel driveway, Country feel! quiet back deck for morning coffee. Large living room, open concept. walk-in closets in all bedrooms. Large master bed and bath with tub and separate shower. Fully furnished . Act quickly and the contract could include a beautiful Ski/fishing boat (presently listed on facebook for $13,500)  8x14 Shed with power and lights.  room sizes are approximate.
